<i>noun</i>: 호우 [호우], 폭주 [폭쭈], 폭우 [포구], 큰비 [큰비] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>호우 [호우]</dt><br>
<dd>heavy rain; downpour</dd><br>
<dd>오랜 시간 내리는 많은 양의 비.</dd><br>
<dd>Rain that falls heavily for a long time.</dd><br>
<dt>폭주 [폭쭈]</dt><br>
<dd>1. downpour; raining hard</dd><br>
<dd>비가 갑자기 많이 쏟아짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of rain pouring down a lot suddenly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. rush; deluge</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 주문 등이 처리하기 힘들 정도로 한꺼번에 몰림.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of many tasks, orders, etc., rushing in all at once, so that it is hard to handle them.</dd><br>
<dt>폭우 [포구]</dt><br>
<dd>heavy rain; downpour</dd><br>
<dd>갑자기 많이 쏟아지는 비.</dd><br>
<dd>Sudden rain that pours down heavily.</dd><br>
<dt>큰비 [큰비]</dt><br>
<dd>heavy rain; downpour</dd><br>
<dd>오랫동안 많이 쏟아지는 비.</dd><br>
<dd>Rain that falls heavily for a long time.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>